{
  "stem": "13981.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- there's-- I didn't show so much, except that I-- like, the lampshades, I actually put them into the courtroom.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did show stills on the projector.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did show films on the projector.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we also made up organizational charts to show how the-- any given unit had been organized and who was the head of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we could nail on the, the defendant with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think this was against-- who was in the east?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I have some on the pictures, there, but I-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] whether it was-- was it Sauckel?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or was it Frank?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I really don't recall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But those were the things we had to--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they were done by people who knew how to do these things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got them into court and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By, by the prosecution, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To display them, yes, against the wall, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pictures, movies taken by, let's say, army-- US Army Signal Corps, of the liberation, of some camps, and of the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] burial, if you want to call it-- such digging trenches and then push the bodies in with bulldozers and have lime put on top of them and then cover them up again.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The lime, of course, was to make the bodies disintegrate faster.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was US Army-- the American--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "US Army Signal Corps.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were provided, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, this was actually shown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes-- Field Marshal Paulus, who had defended Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were, as I remember, around 300,000 German troops there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when the Russian came back to attack af-after they had defended Moscow and the Germans were forced to withdraw in the north, the-- they had more troops available.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
